{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"main_6_level_main_06-02_beg","storyGroup":"main_6","storySort":3,"storyDependence":"main_6_level_main_06-01_end","storyCanShow":0,"storyCode":"6-2","storyName":"一些误会","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"被灰喉勾起的过往回忆让煌产生了一些想法。\n不过当务之急还是应对眼前的整合运动。\n","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"obt/main/level_main_06-02_beg","avgTag":"行动前","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"main_06-02","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":1,"next":3,"characters":["Rosmontis","Scout","Ace","煌","整合运动成员","近卫局成员"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","text":"第二关（后）","id":0},{"type":"dialog","id":1},{"type":"character","id":2},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":3},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/5a/Avg_bg_bg_corridor.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":4},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":5},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$m_dia_street_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta3_181101/m_dia_street_loop.mp3","volume":"0.8","crossfade":"1.5","delay":"0.5","id":6,"musicid":0},{"type":"character","id":7},{"type":"text","text":"咦......Rosmontis，你在做什么？","id":8},{"type":"dialog","id":9},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":10},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":11},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Rosmontis","text":"我......我想修好这个便携终端。","id":12,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Rosmontis","text":"六年前到去年的记忆我都记在这里了......","id":13,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Rosmontis","text":"今天早上，我想读六月十二号记录的时候，屏幕突然就不亮了。","id":14,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Rosmontis","text":"如果......如果真的再读不了......","id":15,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Rosmontis","text":"三月十四号和爸爸去植物园，七月的登山，还有第四个四月，妈妈......","id":16,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Rosmontis","text":"......妈妈......","id":17,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":18},{"type":"character","id":19},{"type":"text","text":"别，别哭！那个啥，你不太擅长用电子屏幕对吧？","id":20},{"type":"text","text":"为什么不等Scout来帮你修一下呢？可露希尔也可以啊？","id":21},{"type":"text","text":"我帮你拿给可露希尔吧，几分钟就搞定啦！","id":22},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","id":23},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Rosmontis","text":"Scout是......","id":24,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Rosmontis","text":"是那个吗，走路很轻的干员吗？","id":25,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"character","id":26},{"type":"text","text":"是他啊！有印象吗？","id":27},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","id":28},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Rosmontis","text":"嗯。","id":29,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Rosmontis","text":"给人很干净的感觉......像白色的瓷砖一样。","id":30,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Rosmontis","text":"他就在那。","id":31,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"character","id":32},{"type":"text","text":"......啊？","id":33},{"type":"dialog","id":34},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_026","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":35},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":36},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Scout","text":"从没听过你对我的评价，现在才知道，原来我感受起来是这么脆弱。","id":37,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/06/Avg_avg_npc_026.png"},{"type":"character","id":38},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.4","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":39},{"type":"text","text":"你什么时候来的？！","id":40},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_026","id":41},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Scout","text":"可以说是一直都在。我习惯隐藏自己了。","id":42,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/06/Avg_avg_npc_026.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","id":43},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Rosmontis","text":"Scout先生他确实一直都在的。","id":44,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Rosmontis","text":"为什么煌没有感觉到呢？","id":45,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"character","id":46},{"type":"text","text":"......我是比较粗线条，没看到啦！","id":47},{"type":"text","text":"不是，你听她说了那么久，怎么不帮她修下啊。","id":48},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_026","id":49},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Scout","text":"抱歉，接下来我们有任务。我得花些精力校准武器。","id":50,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/06/Avg_avg_npc_026.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Scout","text":"你可能要请可露希尔或是机械师Mechanist先生去解决了。","id":51,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/06/Avg_avg_npc_026.png"},{"type":"character","id":52},{"type":"text","text":"是那个，营救Dr.{@nickname}的任务吗？","id":53},{"type":"dialog","id":54},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":55},{"type":"character","name":"char_014_riope","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":56},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":57},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Ace","text":"是。","id":58,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/95/Avg_char_014_riope.png"},{"type":"character","id":59},{"type":"text","text":"哦哦，你也来了。","id":60},{"type":"character","name":"char_014_riope","id":61},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Ace","text":"作为主要发起人之一，如果我自己都不去，罗德岛精英干员不是成了笑话？","id":62,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/95/Avg_char_014_riope.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_026","name2":"char_014_riope","focus":"1","id":63},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Scout","text":"阿斯卡纶怎么回复你的？","id":64,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/06/Avg_avg_npc_026.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_026","name2":"char_014_riope","focus":"2","id":65},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Ace","text":"一样的托辞。她不会参与。同往常一样，她一直都和凯尔希站一边。","id":66,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/95/Avg_char_014_riope.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_026","name2":"char_014_riope","focus":"1","id":67},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Scout","text":"......你有没有考虑过，现在可能不是最佳时机？","id":68,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/06/Avg_avg_npc_026.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_026","name2":"char_014_riope","focus":"2","id":69},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Ace","text":"但这也可能是我们最后的机会。","id":70,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/95/Avg_char_014_riope.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Ace","text":"为了躲避这次天灾，切尔诺伯格很可能会在驶离这里后，转向乌萨斯腹地。在乌萨斯内部展开营救，成功的概率趋近于零。","id":71,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/95/Avg_char_014_riope.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":72},{"type":"character","id":73},{"type":"text","text":"听你们说了那么多回，这个Dr.{@nickname}真有那么神奇吗？","id":74},{"type":"character","name":"char_014_riope","id":75},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Ace","text":"和阿米娅与凯尔希一样神奇。","id":76,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/95/Avg_char_014_riope.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_014_riope","name2":"avg_npc_042","focus":"2","id":77},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Rosmontis","text":"我见过博士吗？","id":78,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_014_riope","name2":"avg_npc_042","focus":"1","id":79},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Ace","text":"没有。不过很快你就能见到了。","id":80,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/95/Avg_char_014_riope.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_014_riope","name2":"avg_npc_042","focus":"2","id":81},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Rosmontis","text":"嗯。我也很想感受一下博士的样子。","id":82,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Rosmontis","text":"很想。","id":83,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_014_riope","name2":"avg_npc_042","focus":"1","id":84},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Scout","text":"你会的，小猫。","id":85,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/95/Avg_char_014_riope.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":86},{"type":"character","id":87},{"type":"text","text":"对了，Ace。 你下辖小队里，有个叫灰喉的非患者。","id":88},{"type":"character","name":"char_014_riope","id":89},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Ace","text":"这事我记得。她应该还在单独舱室接受指导。","id":90,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/95/Avg_char_014_riope.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Ace","text":"煌，听我一句。我带着她几个月了，她也许不太会表达，但绝对没有恶意。","id":91,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/95/Avg_char_014_riope.png"},{"type":"character","id":92},{"type":"text","text":"但她对我的队员说：“我不知道你们感染者有多痛苦。”","id":93},{"type":"character","name":"char_014_riope","id":94},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Ace","text":"我清楚。但她可能真的只是很疑惑，她想要去问这个问题。","id":95,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/95/Avg_char_014_riope.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Ace","text":"我没资格要求干员立即明白我们的处境，而且，灰喉从没质疑过罗德岛的命令。","id":96,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/95/Avg_char_014_riope.png"},{"type":"character","id":97},{"type":"text","text":"其他我不管，我绝对不允许任何人侮辱我的队员，更别说诋毁罗德岛感染者们的奋斗了。","id":98},{"type":"character","name":"char_014_riope","id":99},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Ace","text":"不是现在。我知道你在克制怒意，但真的，不是现在。","id":100,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/95/Avg_char_014_riope.png"},{"type":"character","id":101},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.4","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"true","id":102},{"type":"text","text":"她当着我的面这么说！","id":103},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_026","id":104},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Scout","text":"大猫，消停些。","id":105,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/06/Avg_avg_npc_026.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Scout","text":"你也有任务在身。","id":106,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/06/Avg_avg_npc_026.png"},{"type":"character","id":107},{"type":"text","text":"......是啊。","id":108},{"type":"text","text":"行吧，回来再处理。","id":109},{"type":"text","text":"谁叫Ace资历比我老呢。","id":110},{"type":"character","name":"char_014_riope","id":111},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Ace","text":"一旦你开始用这种口气说话，我就怀疑你是想戏弄别人。","id":112,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/95/Avg_char_014_riope.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_014_riope","name2":"avg_npc_026","focus":"2","id":113},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Scout","text":"她可能真的在取笑你。","id":114,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/06/Avg_avg_npc_026.png"},{"type":"character","id":115},{"type":"text","text":"他只要有两天没修胡子，我就一定会觉得他资历特别老。","id":116},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","name2":"char_014_riope","focus":"1","id":117},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Rosmontis","text":"Ace，胡子很硬。","id":118,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_014_riope","id":119},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Ace","text":"......啊。","id":120,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/9/95/Avg_char_014_riope.png"},{"type":"character","id":121},{"type":"text","text":"哈哈哈。那我去帮她送东西了。我也有任务在身，先走啦。","id":122},{"type":"text","text":"等我任务结束回来，我们再去好好喝一场吧！","id":123},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_026","id":124},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Scout","text":"可别再喝得吐一地了。","id":125,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/06/Avg_avg_npc_026.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Scout","text":"Misery擦了两小时地板，再让他见那种场面，他恐怕也要吐出来。","id":126,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/06/Avg_avg_npc_026.png"},{"type":"character","id":127},{"type":"text","text":"谁知道你酒量那么好啊！","id":128},{"type":"text","text":"Rosmontis，机械师过会儿就把终端给你送过来。","id":129},{"type":"text","text":"乖乖等着就好了，别把这事儿忘了哦！","id":130},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","id":131},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Rosmontis","text":"嗯，我不会忘的！再见！","id":132,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_026","id":133},{"type":"dialogue","name":"Scout","text":"小心烫伤！","id":134,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/06/Avg_avg_npc_026.png"},{"type":"character","id":135},{"type":"text","text":"不会啦，自己的法术，我有分寸的啦！","id":136},{"type":"dialog","id":137},{"type":"character","id":138},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":139},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":140},{"type":"character","id":141},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/20/Avg_bg_bg_building_3.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":142},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":143},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$darkness02_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_darkness02_loop.mp3","volume":"0.8","crossfade":"3","delay":"0.5","id":144,"musicid":1},{"type":"character","name":"char_017_homura_3#5","id":145},{"type":"dialogue","name":"煌","text":"......怎么会变成你们先走一步？","id":146,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/83/Avg_char_017_homura_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"煌","text":"Ace，灰喉这样的非感染者，真的值得你去培育吗？","id":147,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/83/Avg_char_017_homura_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"煌","text":"我们能得到多少信任，又能奉献出多少信任？","id":148,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/83/Avg_char_017_homura_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"煌","text":"如果博士......","id":149,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/83/Avg_char_017_homura_5.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":150},{"type":"character","id":151},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"0.9","id":152},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":153},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"155","text":"你要说什么？！"},"2":{"id":"158","text":"......"},"3":{"id":"161","text":"如果我也不相信罗德岛的话？"}},"values":[],"id":154},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":155,"end":157},{"type":"character","name":"char_017_homura_3#4","id":156},{"type":"dialogue","name":"煌","text":"要说你的坏话。当面说。","id":157,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/df/Avg_char_017_homura_1.png"},{"type":"predicate","references":["2"],"id":158,"end":160},{"type":"character","name":"char_017_homura_3#4","id":159},{"type":"dialogue","name":"煌","text":"如果博士已经来了，那就赶紧出来，别偷偷摸摸的，想躲在墙角不被发现是需要技术的。","id":160,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/df/Avg_char_017_homura_1.png"},{"type":"predicate","references":["3"],"id":161,"end":163},{"type":"character","name":"char_017_homura_3#4","id":162},{"type":"dialogue","name":"煌","text":"那我就把你吊在电线杆上做整合运动的诱饵。放心！不会死的，也就多中几箭吧，开个刀就好了！","id":163,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/df/Avg_char_017_homura_1.png","end":true},{"type":"useless","references":["1","2","3"],"id":164},{"type":"character","name":"char_017_homura_3#4","id":165},{"type":"dialogue","name":"煌","text":"......唉。","id":166,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/df/Avg_char_017_homura_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"煌","text":"唉！","id":167,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/df/Avg_char_017_homura_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"煌","text":"阿米娅让你来的？","id":168,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/df/Avg_char_017_homura_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"煌","text":"好了别说了。她就这点最好，也就这点最不好......","id":169,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/df/Avg_char_017_homura_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"煌","text":"我时时想做些什么提醒下她，让她想想“她还只是个孩子”这种事......每每都适得其反。","id":170,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/df/Avg_char_017_homura_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"煌","text":"只要她还领导着罗德岛，是不是就不可能把她那个小大人架子放下来？哎。","id":171,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/df/Avg_char_017_homura_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"煌","text":"当然，如果不是阿米娅让你来，而是你主动要来陪我什么的，我是不会反感的。","id":172,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/df/Avg_char_017_homura_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"煌","text":"......拖后腿？放心吧，带着三个你我都能行动自如，别说只一个Dr.{@nickname}了。","id":173,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/df/Avg_char_017_homura_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"煌","text":"哎，你看那边。","id":174,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/df/Avg_char_017_homura_1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":175},{"type":"character","id":176},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":177},{"type":"character","id":178},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/20/Avg_bg_bg_building_3.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":179},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":180},{"type":"character","id":181},{"type":"dialogue","name":"整合运动成员","text":"为什么不走！你们走啊！我们不想打了！","id":182},{"type":"dialogue","name":"近卫局成员","text":"唔......我们不会向感染者屈服！","id":183},{"type":"dialogue","name":"整合运动成员","text":"你们就几个人，为什么要这么做，有什么好处！","id":184},{"type":"dialogue","name":"近卫局成员","text":"这是职责！","id":185},{"type":"dialogue","name":"整合运动成员","text":"那就不要怪我们下手狠了！你没看到我们背后那些怪物吗！快些逃啊！！","id":186},{"type":"dialogue","name":"近卫局成员","text":"哪有什么怪物？！","id":187},{"type":"dialog","id":188},{"type":"character","id":189},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":190},{"type":"character","id":191},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/20/Avg_bg_bg_building_3.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":192},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":193},{"type":"character","name":"char_017_homura_3#4","id":194},{"type":"dialogue","name":"煌","text":"看到那批正在穿小巷的整合运动没？他们好像在进攻龙门人的阵线欸。那几个龙门人应该撑不太久......","id":195,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/df/Avg_char_017_homura_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"煌","text":"给我规划条路线呗。","id":196,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/df/Avg_char_017_homura_1.png"},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"198","text":"正常的还是......"}},"values":["2","3"],"id":197},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":198,"end":203},{"type":"character","name":"char_017_homura_3#8","id":199},{"type":"dialogue","name":"煌","text":"当然是最快的啦！","id":200,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_char_017_homura_8.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"煌","text":"别那个表情嘛。扛着你跳上跳下，这也不是第一次了。","id":201,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_char_017_homura_8.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"煌","text":"好！把那群整合运动揍趴下，顺带帮一把那些龙门人吧！","id":202,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_char_017_homura_8.png"},{"type":"delay","time":"0.3","id":203,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":204},{"type":"blocker","block":"true","id":205},{"type":"image","id":206}],"characters":["Rosmontis","Scout","Ace","煌","整合运动成员","近卫局成员"]}